.TH NTFSINFO 8 "Feb 2004" "ntfsprogs version 1.9.0"
.SH NAME
ntfsinfo \- dump a file's attributes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ntfsinfo
.I -d device
.I -i inode-number
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ntfsinfo
will dump the attributes of inode
.IR inode-number .
Run ntfsinfo without arguments for a full list of options.
.PP
